<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n18127c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n18" href="#n18127c">N18 (VI.B.8)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n18all.htm#n18127c"> 127(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Littlejohn hanged / on Arbour hill / eminence</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">In 1189, on the breaking up of Robin Hood&apos;s company, his great companion, <mark>little John</mark>, is said to have exhibited his feats of archery on this green, until, having been detected in a robbery, he <mark>was hanged on the eminence now called Arbour Hill</mark>. <small> John D'Alton, <a name="JDTH" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#JDTH"><cite title="source">The History of County Dublin</cite></a> (1838) 517</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
